dct_title_s: Union County, New Jersey highways, map 4
dct_description_sm: General highway map of Union County. Sheet four of a nine plate map. Prepared by the New Jersey State Highway Department, Division of Planning in cooperation with the U. S. Department of Commerce, Bureau of Public Roads. State highways (including proposed roads) are as of Dec. 31, 1967.
